{"tid":677730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁錦松:本港長遠需要1000萬以上人口","createTime":"2018-05-25T12:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T09:32:36.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a1efc16f528fa75f16143cc25f0580cd00576bd4","tid":677730,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:36:23.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】本港近年面對的競爭加劇，前財政司司長梁錦松表示，本港長遠需要有1000萬人以上人口，才能支持整個大灣區、甚至是整個中國的發展。<br />\n<br />\n梁錦松接受團結香港基金Facebook專頁「政策&bull;正察」訪問時強調，支持發展不僅是為他人，也是為了自己，因為現時知識經濟最能推動經濟發展，本港一方面培養人才，另一方面亦能吸收全世界的精英在香港發展，便能為年青人提供機會。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，香港應該扮演中國境內的環球金融中心和國際人才中心，之後就可以發展金融業和各種創新產業，包括生物科技、創意產業，「所以我們提『三創』，創新、創意、創業，而國家只提『雙創』，但我們高舉『創意』，因為這個最適合香港，因為香港有自由，有知識產權保護，有國際化、開放的環境去發展創意。」<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，本港的醫療依然是世界上最有效，而香港現在至少有4間大學全球排名100名之內，相信高端醫療和高等教育亦可為國家、為香港開創前途，若能配合研究和創科，是可以推動到經濟發展。"},{"pid":"61b6d598ca01903af5ef6788d02bafebfe889366","tid":677730,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"所以我們提『三創』，創新、創意、創業，而<span style=\"color: red;\">國家只提『雙創』</span>，但我們高舉『創意』，因為這個最適合香港，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為香港有自由，有知識產權保護，有國際化、開放的環境去發展創意</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fb75907f9e1a9ef5eef062653c28b0d23ce502","tid":677730,"uid":33352,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"解決左房屋問題先再講1000萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f9e19cb195707a88e359f73cc39d6cccf926f81","tid":677730,"uid":15880,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/204255_643779057f89d79e0528b38ab2eb5cfb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F204255_643779057f89d79e0528b38ab2eb5cfb.gif&h=e80e6f73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"820591e2ee3b7834d205d475515cf9c8106a7908","tid":677730,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話香港已經冇咁重要？<br />\n深圳，上海，仲有個幾個「第二個香港」呢"},{"pid":"4ac99df12a5344087df8d6b2258e134c04bbecbc","tid":677730,"uid":171901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"梁錦松<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你以為你講野仲可以影響香港人心情咩！癌細胞已經係你幾個囝囡身上擴散喇,  你準備你啲家事好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4809c76bd8d23618cecd49108c83da7b9676c09a","tid":677730,"uid":10692,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41b7827de9c3df15818733b90a570385db9d54c8","tid":677730,"uid":34927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得香港得500萬人先解決到房屋醫療退休保障等等既壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人材創意呢啲同人數多寡真係咁大關係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788a6ca0e9f7864a8da9bc09496f05124899e9da","tid":677730,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:40:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母！"},{"pid":"c54829ade5d31714ba81df3e144c984d7a02e1f6","tid":677730,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T16:42:02.000Z","msg":"又要共享港畜榮華"},{"pid":"dd9d5f0302b60c9fc6dc03a5ac36e4f2257b4d2a","tid":677730,"uid":56954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"1000萬人口 冇問題<br />\n你叫中國割多個兩個九龍半島size既平地比香港做殖民地先啦"},{"pid":"b42e9ee5b32aadf1bf81e93aeae3632ec0acf832","tid":677730,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"住係你屋企?"},{"pid":"917